tool_name: CDC Disease or Condition of the Week
tool_description: An API that pulls the CDC's Disease or Condition of the Week. This allows developers to include this information easily, while linking to the CDC's source.
title: CDC Disease or Condition of the Week

api_list.name: Get Current Disease/Condition of the Week
api_list.description: This endpoint will return the current week's Disease or Condition of the Week from the CDC's website.
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://cdc-disease-or-condition-of-the-week.p.rapidapi.com/"

headers = {
    "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
    "X-RapidAPI-Host": "cdc-disease-or-condition-of-the-week.p.rapidapi.com"
}

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)

print(response.json())
